{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_XX01_180.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...That's my advice. Just watch the high notes, and keep it even... Lalala... Just like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Lalala... I see. Thank you, that's very helpful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Cory!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sophie. What's the matter...? Is something wrong with the items I delivered?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "No, I just wanted to ask you something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you look like you've struck inspiration, Sophie. Your eyes are twinkling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I hope you're ready, Corneria. She's going to bombard you with questions."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x20,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I welcome the opportunity...! Ask me anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Thanks. I really appreciate it. Um, I wanted to ask you about duplication..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Duplication...? What Corneria uses to multiply items, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... So, Cory... How do you do it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, well... How I visualize it, is that I try to stretch the item out, then snap it in two."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Stretch, then snap. Pull it out like elastic, then let it break..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? I can kind of imagine that... But can you really duplicate items that way?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yes... But the real trick is in how you make that snap."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "You can't snap it too strongly, or it won't work."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "And it also means you will end up paying a steep price. So you have to snap it just right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Gently, gently... But not too gently, either, or it won't break..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry, Corneria. I'm not sure I follow anymore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Really...? It is quite hard to explain..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Stretch, then snap... Okay, I've got it! I've got it, Cory!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "What?! You actually understood that?!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Uh, yeah. It was pretty straightforward."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I see... That's alchemists for you, I guess. Or maybe it's just Sophie that's special..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "No, no, Cory's explanation was perfect. And now... Yes, I think this'll work!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Cory! See you later, Monika!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Sh-She's gone... I guess she really was here just to ask about duplication..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "It seems so... Hehe, that's so like her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, that's true. Now, back to what I was saying before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Oh, yes. Lalala... What do I do after that...?"
        }
    ]
}